1.title: I'm Man-Arctica!/No Toy Story
1.plot: After a hard day, Man-Arctica takes a pit stop at the Fanlair, but quickly realizes his two biggest fans don't recognize who he is! /When Fanboy and Chum Chum think that playing with toys is for babies, they vow to stop playing with all toys...FOREVER!

2.title: Game Boy/Crib Notes
2.plot: When Boog leaves his precious Chimp Chomp unguarded, Fanboy and Chum Chum seize the opportunity to finally play the game! Kyle is studying hard for his Milkweed Admittance Test, but the boys thwart his efforts by releasing Professor Flan.

3.title: Schoolhouse Lock/Back from the Future
3.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum get locked in school on the last day before summer vacation! Will they escape with their minds intact before they miss the entire summer?

4.title: Tooth or Scare/The Big Bopper
4.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum accidentally cause Kyle to lose a tooth, which means the Wizard Tooth Fairy is coming. But unlike the normal Tooth Fairy, when the Wizard Tooth Fairy comes, he takes all your teeth.

5.title: Present Not Accounted For/The Sword in the Throne
5.plot: It's Chum Chum's birthday and Chum Chum is certain that Fanboy is going to get him the best present ever because that's what he does every year!/While playing in the school's oldest bathroom, Fanboy pulls a bejeweled plunger out of a gilded toilet.

6.title: Brain Freeze
6.plot: After losing their memories from a wicked brain freeze, Fanboy and Chum Chum must retrace their steps to locate their missing underwear.

7.title: Slime Day/Boog Zapper
7.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum can't figure out how to get slimed on Slime Day, because they don't know the secret phrase. So they travel to the Nickelodeon studio to get the secret phrase from the president of the company./Fed up with Boog's bullying, Fanboy builds up an electric charge so he can shock Boog.

8.title: Risky Brizness/Kids in the Hall
8.plot: When Oz's cousin, Brizwald, comes to town, Oz is certain he's after his most valuable Man-Arctica comic book. After all, Briz has made a living off of selling toys.

9.title: Field Trip of Horrors/Frosty Mart Dream Vacation
9.plot: Lenny desperately wants to win the "Frosty Mart Dream Vacation," but sure enough, Fanboy and Chum Chum win it instead. However, the boys think the dream vacation is actually in the Frosty Mart.

10.title: There Will Be Shrieks
10.plot: Fanboy & Chum Chum hit the streets for the ultimate night of treats, but find themselves getting the ultimate trick instead! A mysterious figure named Mr. Trick dupes the boys into eating a magical piece of candy that steals away all their taste forever!

11.title: Igloo of Irritation/HypnotOZed
11.plot: After turning the Fanlair into a rocket ship, Fanboy and Chum Chum crash land next door to their favorite superhero, Man-Arctica!

12.title: Robo-mance/Rattleskunkupine!
12.plot: After Dollar-nator breaks up with a video game, he turns to Fanboy & Chum Chum to help him find someone to grow obsolete with.Something weird has happened to Oz. He's selling his collectibles! The boys try to find out where he got the idea.

13.title: Bubble Trouble/Lucky Chums
13.plot: Boog is all geared up and ready to meet Jay Mitchell, the best Chimp Chomp player in the world and his idol. But before he can get out of his apartment, he's overcome by an allergy attack and has to stay inside his bubble!

14.title: The Last Strawberry Fun Finger/Power Out
14.plot: Fanboy & Chum Chum split a two-pack of Strawberry Fun Fingers. Except, they open the package to find a bonus Fun Finger! The boys are going to watch a movie, but movies from the future require tons of power & the town suffers a blackout because of it.

15.title: Dental Illness/Champ of Chomp
15.plot: Fanboy has a terrible toothache, so Chum Chum has no choice but to bring him to the dentist. Fanboy protests and struggles, despite Chum Chum's assurances that Dr. Plaqula is a fun dentist.

16.title: Get You Next Time/Lice Lice Baby
16.plot: When Fanboy fails to pay a quarter to Retchy Lintpockets, a creepy kid selling taffy, Retchy vows to "get him next time." Suddenly Fanboy finds himself cursed by Retchy at every turn!

17.title: A Very Brrr-y Icemas
17.plot: Man-Arctica travels the world & delivers gifts to all the good kids. Fanboy thinks he is going to get the best toy - the Super Mega Octo Rocket Kraken ("Smork"). But Fanboy learns that his status is more "naughty" than nice!

18.title: Funny Face/Put That Cookie Down!
18.plot: After Fanboy creates the perfect goofy face, he is determined to use it to make the class photo hilarious. Lenny bakes Chocolatonium chip cookies for Agent Johnson's birthday and orders Dollar-nator to keep them away from Fanboy and Chum Chum at all costs

19.title: Two Tickets to Paladise/The Winners
19.plot: One day, Fanboy and Chum Chum wake up and realize they are perfectly in sync. They say, think, and do everything exactly the same!

20.title: Hex Games/Speed Eraser
20.plot: The boys get their hands on a new video game, "Sigmund the Sorcerer's Wiizard Challenge!" Kyle is uninterested and scoffs at Sigmund's merchandazzle ... until he finds out the winner of the game gets admittance to Milkweed Academy.

21.title: Heroes vs. Villains/Face-Eating Aliens from Planet X
21.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum get into an argument over which is better: heroes or villains. Chum Chum thinks heroes are better but Fanboy insists it's all about villains.

22.title: The Cold Rush/Camp-Arctica
22.plot: We travel back to the old west, where Lenwig (Lenny) is trying to run his dry goods store, but prospectors Faniel (Fanboy) and Chumtholemew (Chum Chum) keep getting in the way with their dreams of striking pink gold.

23.title: Normal Day/Buddy Up
23.plot: Mr. Mufflin's class is going on a field trip to the dinosaur museum but when it comes time to "buddy up," Kyle is without a buddy. Fanboy and Chum Chum take it upon themselves to be Kyle's buddy but Kyle takes it too seriously.

24.title: Freezy Freaks/Microphonies
24.plot: When Boog has to dress up as a giant Frosty Freezy Freeze, the boys think he's actually Freezy, the lovable Frosty Freezy Freeze mascot.

25.title: Super Chums
25.plot: Super Chum and Fannihilator have been Best Nemeses since the beginning of time, but when a new supervillain, Copy Kitten, comes along, she vows to stop at nothing to become Super Chum's arch nemesis.

26.title: Secret Club/Attack of the Clones
26.plot: When Fanboy has to stay in detention while the class goes on a field trip, the boys decide to make clones of themselves to stay behind. But things get out of hand when the clones start making clones of clones!

1.title: Wiz Boy/Pick a Nose
1.plot: There's a new kid at school (Kyle) and Fanboy & Chum Chum are determined to show their new friend a great time.Fanboy and Chum Chum agree to swap noses for Class Picture Day, but Fanboy gets jealous of the attention Chum Chum suddenly receives.

2.title: The Janitor Strikes Back/Dollar Day
2.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum have a new best friend made of gum. Fanboy and Chum Chum can?t wait to spend their only dollar on two delicious Frosty Freezy Freezes

3.title: Trading Day/The Hard Sell
3.plot: In a moment of weakness, Fanboy agrees to trade Chum Chum for one of Yo's awesome toys.Oz's mom insists he sell one of his beloved collectibles by day's end, or she will get rid of them all and turn his store into a yogurt shop.

4.title: Digital Pet Cemetery/Fanboy Stinks
4.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum accidentally "power down" Yo's digital pet cat.Fanboy refuses to bathe and he gets so dirty that his suit, "Stinks," actually comes to life.

5.title: I, Fanbot/Berry Sick
5.plot: Desperate not to fail a test, Fanboy decides to switch brains with a robot. During a summer heat wave, the boys discover the Frosty Freeze machine is on the fritz.

6.title: Chimp Chomp Chumps/Precious Pig
6.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum are happily waiting in line for movie tickets when Boog arrives and ruins everything.Fanboy is devastated when he is stripped of his class pet privileges and he will do anything to be reunited with Precious, the class pig.

7.title: Fangboy/Monster in the Mist
7.plot: Fanboy is convinced he was bitten by a vampire and Chum Chum wants to be a vampire, too. Boog mistakenly thinks he sees a monster on the loose in the Frosty Mart and has to rely on Fanboy and Chum Chum to keep him safe.

8.title: Brain Drain/Fanboyfriend
8.plot: Following a particularly awesome crash landing, Fanboy's brain pops out of his head and he loses his memory./Fanboy is practicing to be a superhero and "saves" damsel in distress, Lupe.

9.title: Chicken Pox/Moppy Dearest
9.plot: Kyle comes down with the chicken pox, and Fanboy and Chum Chum are certain they can help cure their wizard pal.Fanboy and Chum Chum are thrilled when they hear that their favorite superhero, Man-Arctica, is going to appear at the school dance.

10.title: Norse-ing Around/The Janitor's Apprentice
10.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum discover a frozen Viking in their icebox and decide to help him ?achieve glory? so he can get into Valhalla.As punishment, Fanboy and Chum Chum are told that they must help Janitor Poopatine clean up the school.

11.title: Excuse Me/Night Morning
11.plot: Fanboy, Chum Chum and Kyle are late for school, but they manage to get Kyle's Elf to write them an excuse note, and it works.Fanboy learns that Chum Chum has discovered a new part of the day called Night Morning.

12.title: Marsha, Marsha, Marsha/Secret Shopper
12.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum wind up in the wrong playground and are mistaken for kindergarteners.Fanboy and Chum Chum take "customer service" to a whole new level when Lenny and Boog leave the Frosty Mart unattended.

13.title: Prank Master/Little Glop of Horrors
13.plot: It?s the boy?s favorite day, Prank Day, and they can?t wait to show off their master pranking skills. Fanboy, Chum Chum and the rest of the kids stage an uprising when the new lunch lady refuses to serve anything but disgusting grey glop.

14.title: Total Recall/Refill Madness
14.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum love their new toy more than anything, despite the fact that it has some strange, and painful, features.Lenny and Boog learn that Fanboy and Chum Chum have a cup that entitles them to endless free refills at the Frosty Mart.

15.title: The Frosty Bus/The Tell-Tale Toy
15.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum can't wait to buy a Frosty Freezy Freeze from the Frosty Bus./Fanboy accidentally breaks one of Chum Chum's brand new toys and is wracked with guilt.

16.title: Cold War/Fanboy in the Plastic Bubble
16.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum catch a cold and they don't just get sick, they get sick of each other.Fanboy and Chum Chum buy Boog's childhood plastic bubble and have the time of their lives.

17.title: Sigmund the Sorcerer/Fanboy A'hoy!
17.plot: When Kyle's old rival, Sigmund the Sorcerer, comes to town, he realizes the value of having friends like Fanboy and Chum Chum./Fanboy and Chum Chum are playing pirates and decide to bury all their favorite possessions so they can then dig up the treasure.

18.title: Fan vs. Wild/The Incredible Shrinking Fanboy
18.plot: Fanboy, Chum Chum and Kyle embark on a camping trip in the great outdoors, also known as the roof of the Frosty Mart./Fanboy thinks he is shrinking and soon will be the size of a thimble.

19.title: Separation Anxiety/Strings Attached
19.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum's inane disruptions finally push their teacher, Mr. Mufflin, to lay down the law and separate their desks./After one bad deed too many, Fanboy is turned into a wooden boy as punishment by a fairy.

20.title: Book Report of the Dead/Stan-Arctica
20.plot: Fanboy uses Kyle's magical Book of the Dead for his book report material and accidentally turns his teacher into a zombie./Fanboy is horrified when his favorite superhero, Man-Arctica, seemingly dies at the hands of a super villain.

21.title: Man-Arctica the Ride/Fanbidextrous
21.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum are extremely excited to ride the new Man-Arctica roller coaster./When Fanboy discovers that people can use BOTH of their hands, he trains his left arm to do everything his right arm can do.

22.title: Saving Private Chum Chum/Jingle Fever
22.plot: Mr. Mufflin takes away everyone's toys in class. Unfortunately this includes taking away Chum Chum!When Fanboy and Chum Chum find out they can win a million Frosty Bucks by writing the new Frosty Mart jingle,

23.title: Eyes on the Prize/Battle of the Stands
23.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum desperately want to find a rare cereal box toy. So they go to Oz for guidance and training./Fanboy and Chum Chum start a lemonade stand, but soon realize Lupe and Yo have a stand of their own... right across the street!

24.title: Lord of the Rings/The Incredible Chulk
24.plot: After Fanboy shows Kyle a simple magic trick, Kyle drives himself crazy trying to figure out how to do it./The boys are shocked when Chum Chum suddenly grows into a humongous Chulk. Maybe now they can get revenge on their bully, Boog.

25.title: Norse Code/The Great Bicycle Mystery
25.plot: Fanboy and Chum Chum are excited when their Viking friend, Thorvald, visits them from Valhalla. Lenny's bike was taken from outside the Frosty Mart! Good thing Fanboy and Chum Chum are on the case.

26.title: A Bopwork Orange/Freeze Tag
26.plot: Boog's gotta learn to stop bopping customers, or he's gonna lose his job.When Man-Arctica comes down to play freeze tag with the kids, they quickly realize he plays by his own rules... which means freezing everyone in sight.

imdb.plot outline: This show is based around two children that dress up as superhero-themed people and go around creating havoc wherever they go, but in the end of some episodes, a resolution is reached, in the other episodes, it ends with a humorous comment. The children are obsessed with a slushy that was inspired by their favorite superhero, Man Arctica. The kids also have many friends that are mentally or physically issued, and have made friends with an adult that lives with his Mom's basement. Fanboy and ChumChum (the kids) usually annoy a store owner (Larry) or a Kid Wizard (Kyle). Fanboy and ChumChum are picked on by Larry's Co-Worker (Boog) and a the school janitor.
